OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy at first. Some
OL,9,Fdrier and clearer spells may develop
OL,10,Fat times overnight, mainly in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAny cloud and rain at first
OL,13,Fwill soon clear to bright or sunny
OL,14,Fspells in the morning. Bright spells
OL,15,Fand a few showers in the afternoon,
OL,16,Fheavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
